<P>
OMB DIRECTOR CONFIRMED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Senate early Friday confirmed Alice Rivlin to be director of the Office of 
Management and Budget.Confirmation came on a voice vote. Rivlin, 63, is the 
first woman to direct the budget office. She fills the vacancy caused when Leon 
E. Panetta left to become White House chief of staff. 
</P>
