<DOCNO> LA100894-0049 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 086588 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 8, 1994, Saturday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
