 Disney Wants to Resume Talks to Buy All of NBC: Negotiations between Walt 
Disney Co. and NBC's parent, General Electric Co., stalled after a $5-billion 
offer from Disney was rejected as too low, people close to the talks said, 
according to Bloomberg Business News.Previously, the sticking point was not 
