</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A shortage of flu vaccine has caused Saddleback Memorial Medical Center to 
postpone a flu clinic originally scheduled for today.A Saddleback spokeswoman 
said the county Health Care Agency was unable to provide the flu vaccine in 
time. 
</P>
