</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Franking charges -- A statement in The Times on Oct. 7 saying that Rep. 
Anthony C. Beilenson used his franking privileges to aid his reelection 
campaign should have been attributed to Richard Sybert, Beilenson's opponent in 
the 24th District race. 
