<TEXT>
<P>
 Saddleback College -- A story Oct. 4 reported that the Saddleback Community 
College District board had approved a 4% yearly pay raise for the faculty, but 
it did not include the vote. The pay hike was approved 6 to 0, with board 
member Teddi Jo Lorch abstaining. 
